phrases: Shit, as if those sisters were not bad enough,
now you are getting in my way, too?
I am tutoring for the Nakanos on Floor 30.
What are you doing out here by yourself?

Not off to a good start.
You are going to tutor us, are not you?
The Quint es sen tial Quin tup let us

I bet you know nothing about fashion!
Teach us Japanese history like you said you would.
I am just going to be studying on my own here, so do not mind me.
but compared to the beginning, this is huge progress.
Be nice to them, and we can reach an understanding.
Still have not given up on tutoring, huh?
I hope you do not fall asleep like you did last time.

Would you like to join us, Nino?
Guess I will have to be content with four for now.
Let us go without her for today.
my acquaintance on the basketball team is looking for someone to fill in for a game.
Why do not you go right now?
Apparently, they only have five members, and one of them broke a bone.
They will not be able to play if they do not find someone.
I feel so bad for them.
They must have practiced so hard.
I cannot just abandon people in need!
That girl does not know how to say no.
Did not you say you had work at two, Ichika?
You should go to a quieter place, like the library or something.
Damn that Nino, always getting in my way...
What is she trying to pull?
You owe me a drink from when you accidentally drank mine.
Okay, let us start the lesson.
All right, let us switch gears.
Why do not we start with the Kamakura period, then?
Since when have you two been so close?
So you have a thing for dull-looking guys, huh?
You are too hung up on looks, Nino.
What is wrong with going for good-looking guys?
Are you telling me it is all about inner beauty?
It is because you do not care about appearances that you can go out dressed so shabbily.
And those pointy nails are supposed to be fashionable?
You would not get it, would you?
I do not even want to.
Do we really need to argue over inner or outer beauty right now?
Why do not we compete on inner beauty, as you say?
Let us have a cooking battle to see who is more homely.
If I win, no studying today.
Y-You are not going to accept, right?
Why is absolutely nothing going my way?
A dutch baby with seasonal veggies and ham.
Well, it is up to you to judge which one's better.
You made it, so you might as well have him eat it.
We fell right into Nino's trap.
I will have to try again another time.
But now it is all clear.
I do not know why, but Nino especially hates me.
I do not feel like I will ever get to be on good terms with her.
If you face her in good faith, she will come around.
What am I supposed to do?
It is your job to figure that out.
Sorry, I forgot my flash cards.
Feel free to come in and grab them.
Wait, Miku, you are okay with that?
You are already out of the shower?!
Come to think of it, she is not one to care about these things.
I will just grab my cards and leave.
I thought you were going to take a bath.
My contacts are on the usual shelf.
Could you get them for me?
Her eyesight is so bad that she cannot see me?
If she finds out I am here, there will be no faith left!
Are you still mad about me messing with you at lunch?
I feel bad about it, okay?
That is not where they are.
They are on the shelf above.
I though they were on this shelf.
He keeps coming into our home just because Dad ordered it.
This home is for us five.
There is no place for him here.
From now on, he is banned from our place!
At that point, I still did not know...
You were great as always today, Ichika-chan.
I did not know how hard it would be to face these five idiots one at a time.
We are lucky to have you.
Let us kill it next time, too.
Hey, I want to ask you something...
Would you be up for officially joining the basketball team?
And I would be taught a lesson, too.
It is because of what she said.
So you have a thing for dull-looking guys, huh?
That I am a complete idiot, too.
I just came to take something.
That is not what I meant!
Your Honor, please have a look at this.
lost control of his urges in front of a young high school girl.
This is you in this photo, is it not?
Absent due to basketball team duties
This guy pretended to leave the apartment
and waited for me to exit the shower.
For his heinous crimes, I request that he be barred permanently from entering here.
I cannot say I approve of your actions.
I just came to get something.
Futaro may look like a criminal, but he is innocent.
What do you mean, I look like a criminal?
I let him in over the intercom.
You are still taking his side?
That he is here to take something!
You mean he forgot something, and he came to get it.
Your Honor, Miku is defending him due to her feelings for him.
I knew you would believe in me, Miku.
Are you acting like that because you are wary of him?
Just so you know, he saw me naked.

Maybe not for you, but there is for me.
Our bodies are about the same.

Even if Miku were right, would you really end up in this position?
This guy threw himself onto me out of nowhere.
Shoot, I need to fight back.
I am going to lose my tutoring job.
But can I get them to believe me?
Some books fell off the the shelves,
and he shielded Nino from them?
If you look carefully, you could see it that way.
I have not done anything for you to thank me.
I am just proposing a possible explanation.
Yeah, there is no way Futaro-kun would have the balls.
Why are you talking like it is been resolved now?
Quit talking out of your ass!
Come on, do not get so heated.
We sisters used to get along so well, remember?
That said, this happened because I was being careless.
I can finally go home and study.
Get this, we are having your favorite: curry udon!
Are they really okay with things as they are?
Guess I should not meddle too much in another family's issues.
She did not bring her key,
but she cannot bring herself to ask the three girls inside?
I do not want to see your face anymore.
She would probably lash out if I helped her.
Go ahead and wait by yourself.
There is a problem I just could not solve.
I do not feel like going home until I solve it.
All you ever care about is studying.
Wait, I guess you could say I am studying because I am stupid.
They have got to be crazy to let a creepy guy like you inside.
This home is for us five.
There is no place for him here.
It cannot be just because you hate me.
Are you sure it is not the opposite?
You love your four sisters, do not you?
That is why you do not like an outsider like me.
Nino, I know how you feel.
I did not do anything wrong, did I?
Why should I have to beat myself up over this?
I have made up my mind.
I am not going to accept you.
Even if that makes the other girls hate me.
Nino, how long are you going to sit here?
Hurry up and get back inside.
But I still need to talk to him.
It looks like it is going to get even harder.
This is why I hate meddling too much.

Nino's in charge of the chores.
